title: Purchasing power change in the Netherlands 2015 to 2020
summary: Overall Year on year percentage change has decreased over the Year.
Year on year percentage change is roughly constant from 2016 to 2018, gradually increasing from 2018 to 2019, and finally roughly constant from 2019 to 2020.
The line significantly decreased by 2.3 from Year 2016 to 2017, and lastly, increased by 1.3 from Year 2018 to 2019.
The highest Year on year percentage change, of value 2.6 was reached at Year 2016
Minimum Year on year percentage change about 0.3 was reached at Year 2017, and 2018
